Customer Conduct</p><p>
Although PaytonSellers will always strive to resolve issues to the satisfaction of the 
customer in a professional, courteous and friendly fashion, we will not tolerate
 any unacceptable or unreasonable behavior towards our Customer Service Team members.
Unacceptable behavior directed towards Customer Service staff or PaytonSellers may, for 
