Excessive number of complaints compared to the total purchase value history.
</p><p>
For such behavior, complainants may be advised and formally notified of the following:
</p><p>
Their language is considered offensive, abusive, threatening, and wholly unacceptable.
They must refrain from using such language, intimidation, and threats.
</p><p>
There will be no further exchange of correspondence on the matter if they persist 
with this behavior.</p><p>
PaytonSellers reserves the right to no longer accept orders from the customer in the 
future without further notice.</p><p>
Complaint Escalation process</p><p>
This process applies strictly to Customer Service issues. For separate legal 
issues such as copyright, please view our legal page here.
If the customer is dissatisfied with the solution offered by our Customer Service,
